{"tid":658742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國暗星康城紅地氈疑扮跌　倒奶出位","createTime":"2018-05-09T08:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T12:06:16.000Z","uid":153228,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"267ce4f44612e41146d7660131e68ded04db32a7","tid":658742,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180509%2Fbkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001.html%3F&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4b1e7036\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001.html?</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/photo/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180509134108\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180509134108&h=3d37874c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/photo/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg?20180509134108\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20180509134108&h=65292e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n康城電影節香港時間今日凌晨開幕，傳媒焦點都在被邀出席的國際明星上，不過紅地氈上有一個谷胸上陣的內地「大媽」被指「不請自來」，還「不小心」摔在地上，裙底走光，不過她剛巧用手袋遮住，被網友質疑是假跌博出位！<br />\n<br />\n該名女子之後立即被起底，原來是名為邢小红的暗星，微博簡介自稱是第18屆環球夫人世界五強、亞洲總冠軍，現居新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n她留言解釋自己跌倒的原因，是大半碼的高跟鞋與選美時斷裂過的腳跟，但她寧願「相信一切是最好的安排。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/photo/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_06b.jpg?20180509134108\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20180509134108&h=e0cbe59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180509/photo/bkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_05p.jpg?20180509134108\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180509124824031-0509_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20180509134108&h=54311913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邢小红與老公結伴到場。"},{"pid":"d40e6e4e373645b7b992c7cab73665381948b303","tid":658742,"uid":153228,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/13697179_752232208213431_4431059755274488760_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F13697179_752232208213431_4431059755274488760_n.jpg&h=a9cf4d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a017642a2f0002fb7b097936e3d561d81fe8c9db","tid":658742,"uid":1069,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"整容樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728fdd5868a72566083aefbaefd1f344107b0431","tid":658742,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"睇住跌甩個下爬呀"},{"pid":"893fa7e04ee1f6904876dd78c29236b4b5cfcfbb","tid":658742,"uid":19287,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/164701_c3e3c214f594f65c44d3376ef95c41dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F164701_c3e3c214f594f65c44d3376ef95c41dd.png&h=18a4c28b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有d似"},{"pid":"fe3594d93cc6c11b7204453fc0dd613a72fc98c0","tid":658742,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:47:15.000Z",